(70741, 1, '2015-11-25 12:11:24', '2015-11-25 12:11:24', '[vc_row type="container" padding_top="" padding_bottom="" css=".vc_custom_1451759148890{margin-top: 30px !important;margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Just fill out this quick form</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][contact-form-7 id="70744"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class=".pl-40"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>What you get</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="#e2e2e2" type="normal" thickness="1" up="" down="18"][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1448459806899{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\n<p class="with-icon"><i class="ion-ios-telephone-outline"></i> A phone call from one of our business consultants</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="#e2e2e2" type="normal" thickness="1" up="" down="18"][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1448460119968{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\n<p class="with-icon"><i class="ion-ios-calculator-outline"></i> A cost estimate of your project based upon your submission</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="#e2e2e2" type="normal" thickness="1" up="" down="18"][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1448460069037{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\n<p class="with-icon"><i class="ion-ios-person-outline"></i> An in-person meeting to discuss the finer details if necessary</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="#e2e2e2" type="normal" thickness="1" up="" down="18"][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1448460028712{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\n<p class="with-icon"><i class="ion-ios-locked-outline"></i> 100% privacy guaranteed, your details are safe and protected</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Get a Quote', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'get-a-quote', '', '', '2015-11-25 12:11:24', '2015-11-25 12:11:24', '', 0, 'http://factory.commercegurus.com/?page_id=70741', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(70744, 1, '2015-11-25 12:13:44', '2015-11-25 12:13:44', '<div class="row">\n\n<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">\n\n<p>Your Name (required)<br />\n    [text* your-name] </p>\n\n<p>Your Email (required)<br />\n    [email* your-email] </p>\n\n<p>Your Phone Number<br />\n[tel your-phone]</p>\n\n<p>Company Name<br />\n    [text company-name] </p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">\n\n<p>Project Title<br />\n    [text project-title] </p>\n\n<p>Your Requirements<br />\n    [textarea your-requirements] </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>[submit "Send"]</p>\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <youremail@gmail.com>\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [project-title]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-requirements]\n\nPhone Number:\n[your-phone]\n\nCompany Name:\n[company-name]\n\n\n--\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Broker(http://broker.commercegurus.com)\nyouremail@gmail.com\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\n[your-subject]\nBroker Demo <wordpress@brokerdemo.commercegurus.com>\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n--\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Broker Demo (http://brokerdemo.commercegurus.com)\n[your-email]\nReply-To: colmtroy@gmail.com\n\n\n\nYour message was sent successfully. Thanks.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nValidation errors occurred. Please confirm the fields and submit it again.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nPlease accept the terms to proceed.\nPlease fill in the required field.\nThis input is too long.\nThis input is too short.\nDate format seems invalid.\nThis date is too early.\nThis date is too late.\nFailed to upload file.\nThis file type is not allowed.\nThis file is too large.\nFailed to upload file. Error occurred.\nNumber format seems invalid.\nThis number is too small.\nThis number is too large.\nYour answer is not correct.\nEmail address seems invalid.\nURL seems invalid.\nTelephone number seems invalid.\nYour entered code is incorrect.', 'Get a Quote', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form_copy', '', '', '2015-11-25 12:13:44', '2015-11-25 12:13:44', '', 0, 'http://factory.commercegurus.com/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&amp;p=70744', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
(70766, 1, '2015-11-26 14:00:53', '2015-11-26 14:00:53', '[vc_row type="container" padding_top="" padding_bottom="" css=".vc_custom_1451769709272{margin-bottom: 20px !important;padding-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Document Archive</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Download and view our brochures and manuals offline. To view them, you may need a PDF reader such as <a href="https://get.adobe.com/reader/">Adobe Acrobat</a> installed on your Mac or PC.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="container" padding_top="" padding_bottom="" css=".vc_custom_1448554138292{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="download" css=".vc_custom_1448899402866{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_raw_html]JTNDaSUyMGNsYXNzJTNEJTIyaW9uLWlvcy1jb3B5LW91dGxpbmUlMjIlM0UlM0MlMkZpJTNF[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1451904052751{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"]\n<h4><a href="#">Material Engineering Brochure</a></h4>\nAn overview of our services, the discovery and design of new materials with an emphasis on solids.\n\n<small style="color: #999999;">~ PDF (180KB)</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="download" css=".vc_custom_1448899411161{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_raw_html]JTNDaSUyMGNsYXNzJTNEJTIyaW9uLWlvcy1jb3B5LW91dGxpbmUlMjIlM0UlM0MlMkZpJTNF[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1451904076649{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"]\n<h4><a href="#">Chemical Research Brochure</a></h4>\nDesigning large-scale processes that convert chemicals, raw materials, living cells, and energy into useful forms.\n\n<small style="color: #999999;">~ PDF (250KB)</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="container" padding_top="" padding_bottom="" css=".vc_custom_1448553755216{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="download" css=".vc_custom_1448899429288{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_raw_html]JTNDaSUyMGNsYXNzJTNEJTIyaW9uLWlvcy1jb3B5LW91dGxpbmUlMjIlM0UlM0MlMkZpJTNF[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1451904086975{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"]\n<h4><a href="#">Agricultural Processing Brochure</a></h4>\nResearch on the natural, economic and social sciences that are used in the practice and understanding of agriculture.\n\n<small style="color: #999999;">~ PDF (210KB)</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="download" css=".vc_custom_1448899436939{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_raw_html]JTNDaSUyMGNsYXNzJTNEJTIyaW9uLWlvcy1jb3B5LW91dGxpbmUlMjIlM0UlM0MlMkZpJTNF[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1451904095305{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"]\n<h4><a href="#">Mechanical Engineering Services</a></h4>\nDesigning and analyzing manufacturing plants, industrial equipment and machinery, heating and cooling systems.\n\n<small style="color: #999999;">~ PDF (230KB)</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="container" padding_top="" padding_bottom="" css=".vc_custom_1448898008970{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="download"][vc_raw_html]JTNDaSUyMGNsYXNzJTNEJTIyaW9uLWlvcy1jb3B5LW91dGxpbmUlMjIlM0UlM0MlMkZpJTNF[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1451904105098{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"]\n<h4><a href="#">Power and Energy Research</a></h4>\nEnergy development endeavor focused on making available sufficient primary energy sources.\n\n<small style="color: #999999;">~ PDF (190KB)</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="download"][vc_raw_html]JTNDaSUyMGNsYXNzJTNEJTIyaW9uLWlvcy1jb3B5LW91dGxpbmUlMjIlM0UlM0MlMkZpJTNF[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1451904113441{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"]\n<h4><a href="#">Petroleum and Gas Services</a></h4>\nThe processes of exploration, extraction, refining, transporting and marketing petroleum products.\n\n<small style="color: #999999;">~ PDF (180KB)</small>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Downloads', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'downloads', '', '', '2015-11-26 14:00:53', '2015-11-26 14:00:53', '', 0, 'http://factory.commercegurus.com/?page_id=70766', 0, 'page', '', 0),
